data.description: Fall in love with this spectacular Central Park home incredibly nestled between Harvest Park, Willow Basin Park, and Willow Bark park—homemade for the city soul and the prairie heart! This sought-after home offers a gorgeous craftsman curb appeal with a covered front porch, 4 bedrooms 4 bathrooms, and 2,832 total SqFt. Perfectly located on a large, park-like courtyard, this Central Park home is only minutes away from I-70, the Shops at Northfield, Conservatory Green, Maverick pool, and in close proximity to Downtown Denver and DIA. Your story begins in this two-story dream home with a bright and open floor plan where you are greeted with a quaint welcoming entrance, an incredible great room with a handsome fireplace open to both the fabulous dining room with beautiful views of your private yard, and open to the fabulous kitchen with slab dine-in granite island, upgraded stainless appliances, powder bath, mudroom, and access to your two-car attached garage. The second level is greeted with an expansive landing, a large master bedroom with a huge walk-in closet and en-suite five-piece master bathroom, two secondary bedrooms, a full bathroom, and upper laundry. The fully finished basement features a huge great room with a gorgeous wet bar, an additional bedroom, 3/4 bathroom, a flex space, and amazing storage. What's more, you will delight in your private, yet inviting yard oasis complete with an oversized concrete patio-perfect for enjoying s'mores or simply relaxing! This lovely home also features plantation shutters, newer paint, slab granite counters, engineered wood floors, and so much more!
